      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "a199",
      "text": "T=0ms: W apasat, predictie x=120, trimite seq=1\nT=16ms: seq=2, predictie x=124\nT=33ms: SERVER TICK -> x=128 autoritate, snapshot seq=3\nT=33ms: reconcile - sterge pending <=3, re-simuleaza rest\nT=66ms: TICK #2 -> x=143\n...\nT=2000ms: eliberezi W, friction opreste gradual",
      "originalText": "T=0ms: W apasat, predictie x=120, trimite seq=1\nT=16ms: seq=2, predictie x=124\nT=33ms: SERVER TICK -> x=128 autoritate, snapshot seq=3\nT=33ms: reconcile - sterge pending <=3, re-simuleaza rest\nT=66ms: TICK #2 -> x=143\n...\nT=2000ms: eliberezi W, friction opreste gradual",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "id000913515",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
