    {
      "id": "id001793143",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 92.0,
      "y": 5353.0,
      "width": 596.0,
      "height": 210.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 438723866,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 82301461,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781253122088,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "a242",
      "text": "FRICȚIUNE:\nspeed = sqrt(vx^2+vy^2)\ncontrol = max(speed, 82)\ndrop = control * 7.4 * dt\nnewSpeed = max(speed-drop, 0)\n\nACCELERARE:\nwishX = cos(a)*fwd - sin(a)*strafe\ncurrentSpeed = vx*wishX + vy*wishY\naccSpeed = min(2550*dt, v_max-current)\nvx += accSpeed*wishX\n\nJUMP: vz=520, vx*=1.09 (bunnyhop)\nAIR: vz -= 1350*dt",
      "originalText": "FRICȚIUNE:\nspeed = sqrt(vx^2+vy^2)\ncontrol = max(speed, 82)\ndrop = control * 7.4 * dt\nnewSpeed = max(speed-drop, 0)\n\nACCELERARE:\nwishX = cos(a)*fwd - sin(a)*strafe\ncurrentSpeed = vx*wishX + vy*wishY\naccSpeed = min(2550*dt, v_max-current)\nvx += accSpeed*wishX\n\nJUMP: vz=520, vx*=1.09 (bunnyhop)\nAIR: vz -= 1350*dt",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "id001787073",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "id001818922",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 732.0,
      "y": 5353.0,
      "width": 556.0,
      "height": 210.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1655477057,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1265990,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781253122088,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "index": "a243",
      "text": "CONSTANTE:\nv_max normal = 460\nv_max sprint = 667 (x1.45)\nv_max crouch = 239 (x0.52)\naccel aer = x0.45\ndt server = 1/30\ndt client = 1/60\n\nt_peak jump = 0.39s\nh_max jump = 100 unitati\n\nGlonț:\nvx = lookDirX * bulletSpeed\nt = clamp(dot/|seg|^2, 0, 1)",
      "originalText": "CONSTANTE:\nv_max normal = 460\nv_max sprint = 667 (x1.45)\nv_max crouch = 239 (x0.52)\naccel aer = x0.45\ndt server = 1/30\ndt client = 1/60\n\nt_peak jump = 0.39s\nh_max jump = 100 unitati\n\nGlonț:\nvx = lookDirX * bulletSpeed\nt = clamp(dot/|seg|^2, 0, 1)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "id001802567",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
